        <!-- FAQ Accordion -->
        <section class="section faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="accordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>What is included in SPIN membership?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                SPIN membership includes access to all educational resources, fellowship programs, research opportunities, networking events, and exclusive member content. Full members receive complete access to all programs, while student/trainee members receive discounted rates and specialized resources for career development.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>How do I qualify for student/trainee membership?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Student/trainee membership is available to medical students, residents, fellows, and other trainees in radiology or related fields. You will need to provide proof of enrollment or training status during the registration process. This membership tier offers significant discounts and specialized resources for career development.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>Can I upgrade from student to full membership?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, you can upgrade from student/trainee membership to full membership at any time. Contact our membership team to process your upgrade. The price difference will be prorated based on your remaining membership period.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>What are the fellowship program requirements?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                The SPIN Fellowship Program requires active SPIN membership and completion of our three-part curriculum: Part 1 (Foundations), Part 2 (Levelling Up), and The Finale (in-person meeting). Each part has specific prerequisites and learning objectives designed to advance your expertise in pediatric neuroradiology.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>How do I access member-only content?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                After completing your membership registration and payment, you will receive login credentials to access the member portal. From there, you can access all educational content, research resources, member directory, and exclusive materials. If you experience any issues, contact our support team.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>Is membership tax-deductible?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                SPIN membership fees may be tax-deductible as professional development expenses. We recommend consulting with your tax advisor or accounting department to determine eligibility based on your specific circumstances. We can provide membership receipts for your records.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>Can my institution pay for multiple memberships?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, we offer institutional membership options for hospitals, universities, and other organizations. Contact our membership team to discuss bulk pricing and institutional billing arrangements. We can also provide purchase orders and institutional invoicing.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <div class="accordion-header">
                            <span>What is the refund policy?</span>
                            <span class="accordion-icon">‚ñº</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                SPIN offers a 30-day money-back guarantee for new memberships. If you are not satisfied with your membership within the first 30 days, contact us for a full refund. Refunds are not available after the 30-day period, but you can choose not to renew for the following year.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
